==English==
===Etymology===
Originated as a slang term in tattoo and piercing parlours in Californian [[counter culture]] but has gained traction in mainstream society and other areas.

===Noun===
'''[[permanent]] [[dirt]]'''

# (''colloquial'') A tattoo
# (''colloquial'') Any form of tattoo, piercing, (deliberate) scarring or other body modification that is considered permanent or would take significant effort to remove.
# (''colloquial'') A hair dye or [[permanent wave]] that must be allowed to grow out or be reversed by repeating the process, that will not wash out.